---
const ALLRIDE_BOOKING_URL =
  "https://dispatch.allrideapps.net/booking-form/5d4212f2-f629-48a1-9b9c-cb816296b00a";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Pricing | Let’s Car’raoke</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="See Let’s Car’raoke package options and book to receive an instant quote via our secure booking form."
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="header">
      <div class="container header-inner">
        <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Home">
          <img
            src="/assets/lets-carraoke.png"
            alt="Let’s Car’raoke logo"
            loading="eager"
            width="200"
            height="100"
          />
        </a>

        <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="Primary">
          <a class="nav-link" href="/services">Services</a>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="page">
      <h1>Pricing</h1>
      <p>
        Choose your experience, then book to receive an instant quote. Final pricing is calculated from your
        route, time, and selected add-ons in the booking form.
      </p>

      <p class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn" href={ALLRIDE_BOOKING_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Book Now (Instant Quote)
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/services">Browse Services</a>
      </p>

      <h2>Packages</h2>

      <section class="cards" aria-label="Pricing packages">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Signature Car’raoke (60 min)</h3>
          <p>Hosted private karaoke ride energy — perfect for birthdays, date nights, pregames, and tourists.</p>
          <p><a class="text-link" href="/services/signature-carraoke-60">View details</a></p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3>Premium Private Car’raoke (90 min)</h3>
          <p>More time. More songs. More celebration. Best when the ride is the main event.</p>
          <p><a class="text-link" href="/services/premium-private-carraoke-90">View details</a></p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3>Luxury / VIP Car’raoke</h3>
          <p>Elevated presentation for premium guests and special occasions.</p>
          <p><a class="text-link" href="/services/luxury-vip-carraoke">View details</a></p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3>Assisted Transportation & Engagement</h3>
          <p>Care-forward rides with patient support, clear communication, and calm engagement when appropriate.</p>
          <p><a class="text-link" href="/services/assisted-transportation-engagement">View details</a></p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3>Private / VIP / Airport</h3>
          <p>Premium private transportation for travelers, executives, and special events.</p>
          <p><a class="text-link" href="/services/private-vip-airport">View details</a></p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <h2>How pricing works</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You select a package, pickup/drop-off, and any add-ons in the booking form.</li>
        <li>The system calculates your quote using distance, time, and selected options.</li>
        <li>Your quote is shown before you confirm the booking.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Service policies</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Private experience (your group only) unless otherwise arranged.</li>
        <li>Rider count must match vehicle capacity for safety.</li>
        <li>Wait time, route changes, or additional stops may adjust the quote.</li>
        <li>We reserve the right to end service for unsafe or disruptive behavior.</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn" href={ALLRIDE_BOOKING_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Book Now (Instant Quote)
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/#contact">Questions? Contact us</a>
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
